         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>b. highlighted letters were read by Sherard, but not subsequently</p>
            <p>c. l.1, <foreign xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xsl:lang="grc">τε</foreign> omitted by Cormack</p>
